Put together a healthy meal plan for me for seven days.  I can't have dairy, garlic, honey, almonds, pistachios, or cashews
Okay, here is your meal plan without dairy, garlic, honey, almonds, pistachio and cashew. Day 1 Breakfast: Oatmeal with berries and walnuts Lunch: Grilled chicken salad with avocado and sunflower seeds Dinner: Baked fish with roasted vegetables Snack: Apple slices with almond butter Day 2 Breakfast: Vegan overnight oats with banana and pecans Lunch: Black bean burger with sweet potato fries Dinner: Roast chicken with mashed potatoes and carrots Snack: Fruit salad with pine nuts Day 3 Breakfast: Quinoa porridge with dried cherries and hazelnut Lunch: Vegan tacos with black beans, corn and salsa Dinner: Baked chicken thighs with roasted potatoes Snack: Fruit salad with pumpkin seeds Day 4 Breakfast: Oatmeal with blueberries and walnuts Lunch: Grilled tofu sandwiches with carrots and hummus Dinner: Chickpea curry with rice and peas Snack: Veggie sticks with sunflower seeds Day 5 Breakfast: Quinoa porridge with dried cherries and hazelnut Lunch: Black bean burger with sweet potato fries Dinner: Baked chicken thighs with roasted potatoes Snack: Fruit salad with pumpkin seeds Day 6 Breakfast: Vegan overnight oats with banana and pecans Lunch: Grilled tofu sandwiches with carrots and hummus Dinner: Chickpea curry with rice and peas Snack: Veggie sticks with sunflower seeds Day 7 Breakfast: Oatmeal with blueberries and walnuts Lunch: Black bean burger with sweet potato fries Dinner: Baked chicken thighs with roasted potatoes Snack: Fruit salad with pumpkin seeds
